title: Extent of Pennsylvania Underlain by Marcellus Shale
name: Extent of Pennsylvania Underlain by Marcellus Shale
description: This data set is derived from the 1:250000 digital bedrock Geology of Pennsylvania (http://www.dcnr.state.pa.us/topogeo/gismaps/digital.aspx). The polygons herein were created by dissolving/merging the polygons for the bedrock geologic units that were younger (overlay) than the Marcellus formation.
